# Loose dependency set for the Shepherd docs pipeline (the input to the lock).
#
# This is the human-edited list. To re-pin after editing it, run from this
# folder (only `uv` required on PATH):
#
#   PYTHONUTF8=1 uv pip compile --no-build docs-requirements.in -o docs-requirements.txt
#
# (add --upgrade to bump within these constraints; add --generate-hashes for
# hash-locked installs — see docs-requirements.txt header). Every entry point
# and the CI job install from the compiled docs-requirements.txt, never from
# this file directly, so builds are reproducible (FINDINGS: deps floated latest).
mkdocs-material
mkdocstrings[python]
pathspec
pyyaml
pytest
ruff
